OL,3,C'I collapsed on mile 24':The dangers
OL,4,Cof taking ibuprofen before a marathon
OL,6,FBy Alice O'Connell, ITV News Assistant
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FMax Laing, 23, ran his first marathon
OL,10,Fin April 2024, but after taking an
OL,11,Fibuprofen tablet to treat knee
OL,12,Fdiscomfort, he collapsed during his
OL,13,Fpenultimate mile and woke up in a
OL,14,Fmedical tent.
OL,16,F"I remember people standing above me,
OL,17,Fbut no faces just voices, trying to
OL,18,Fexplain to me what they were doing and
OL,19,Fwhy I was submerged in an ice jacket",
OL,20,FMax explained.
