OL,3,C'I collapsed on mile 24':The dangers
OL,4,Cof taking ibuprofen before a marathon
OL,6,FOn-site medics were concerned about
OL,7,FMax's temperature and tried to reduce
OL,8,Fit before taking him to hospital.
OL,10,FMax was then rushed to A&E where he
OL,11,Fwas treated by heat exertion
OL,12,Fspecialists before being placed in an
OL,13,FIntensive Care Unit for seven days.
OL,15,F"(They) took me to the Intensive Care
OL,16,FUnit as they were aware of the serious
OL,17,Fdecline my body was about to suffer",
OL,18,FMax said.
