OL,3,C'I collapsed on mile 24':The dangers
OL,4,Cof taking ibuprofen before a marathon
OL,6,F"I had to train my body to walk and do
OL,7,Fsmall mobility movements for a long
OL,8,Fwhile after," he said.
OL,10,F"I am very lucky to be alive given the
OL,11,Fextreme circumstances, so am forever
OL,12,Fgrateful to the people who helped me
OL,13,Falong the way".
OL,15,FResearchers still don't fully
OL,16,Funderstand how non-steroidal anti-
OL,17,F inflammatory drugs (NSAIDs), like
OL,18,Fibuprofen, interact with endurance
OL,19,Fevents, like marathons, and heat.
