OL,3,C'I collapsed on mile 24':The dangers
OL,4,Cof taking ibuprofen before a marathon
OL,6,FMore than 56,000 people are expected
OL,7,Fto run the TCS London Marathon on
OL,8,FApril 27th.
OL,10,FDr Dan Fitzpatrick, a marathon runner
OL,11,Fhealth and concussion researcher, will
OL,12,Fbe there gathering as much data as he
OL,13,Fcan on runners, like Max, who collapse.
OL,15,FDr Fitzpatrick has been studying
OL,16,Fmarathon runners for the past five
OL,17,Fyears. He believes a 'perfect storm'
OL,18,Fof conflicting factors contributes to
OL,19,Fcompetitors collapsing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
