OL,3,C'I collapsed on mile 24':The dangers
OL,4,Cof taking ibuprofen before a marathon
OL,6,F"The main worry we have is acute
OL,7,Fkidney and acute liver failure, which
OL,8,Fcan mean that you need to go to
OL,9,Fintensive care and have a kidney
OL,10,Freplacement. And that's what we want
OL,11,Fto help prevent," said Dr Fitzpatrick.
OL,13,F"So if they've had like a virally kind
OL,14,Fof cough or cold or if they've had
OL,15,Flike a tummy bug, all those things can
OL,16,Fcreate a perfect storm.
OL,18,F"That means that our body's way of
OL,19,Fmanaging with being a bit dehydrated
OL,20,Fis putting a bit of extra stress on
OL,21,Fthe kidneys," he said.
