OL,3,C'I collapsed on mile 24':The dangers
OL,4,Cof taking ibuprofen before a marathon
OL,6,FHe explained that ibuprofen tablets
OL,7,Faren't the only option for treating
OL,8,Fpre-marathon pain.
OL,10,F"Paracetamol is a really good
OL,11,Fpainkiller. And something like
OL,12,Fibuprofen or like a volterol gel.
OL,14,F"The amounts of those drugs that get
OL,15,Fabsorbed into your body overall is
OL,16,Freally low. But the amounts that gets
OL,17,Fabsorbed into the area you put them is
OL,18,Fstill quite good. So actually they're
OL,19,Foften quite effective," said Dr
OL,20,FFitzpatrick.
